Hey VIMAGERS! We have great news for you! Animating your photos with VIMAGE From now on it s not only a dream! Let s try out our new Flow feature and make your images live! Just draw on the area you would like to see to move and set the direction. Besides the flow animator we improved the app with size optimization and accurate live preview as well! We hope you ll love the new features!
